## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="391c6-103">次のタイプ ライブラリで`OLE_COLOR`のエイリアス`int`です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="391c6-103">In the following type library,  `OLE_COLOR` is an alias for `int`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="391c6-104">引数のインポート中に、`Color`アクセサーが付いて、<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComAliasNameAttribute>とそのタイプ ライブラリの参照を示すために`OLE_COLOR`です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="391c6-104">During import, the arguments of the `Color` accessor are marked with the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComAliasNameAttribute> to indicate that type library refers to them as `OLE_COLOR`.</span></span>  

```  

typedef int OLE_COLOR;    

interface Baz {  
 HRESULT SetColor([in] OLE_COLOR cl);  
 HRESULT GetColor([out, retval] OLE_COLOR *cl);  
}  

```  

